The evidence with the title 'Tuition costs of colleges and universities ' says The price for undergraduate tuition, fees, room, and board at private for-profit institutions decreased 16 percent between 2005–06 and 2015–16 , after adjustment for inflation . SOURCE: U.S. Department Of Education, National Center For Education  ... By level and control of institution : selected years, 1984–85 to 2015–16 . 
